 // found in the LICENSE file.
+// GHOSTIUM-HOOK-ANCHOR: Spec-E navigator_ua_data.cc surfaces.
+//   NavigatorUAData::brands / mobile / platform / getHighEntropyValues
+//   consult the cached profile via FingerprintNoiseSource. The
+//   WebContents-level UA override (Spec-C EmulationBridge) is the
+//   primary path; this hook covers fallbacks. See
